headline.print_headline: Vinci, Nara, Pliskova Make Istanbul Quarters
headline.main: Vinci, Nara, Pliskova Make Istanbul Quarters

lead_paragraph: Second-seeded Roberta Vinci of Italy advanced to the Istanbul Cup quarterfinals when Romanian qualifier Alexandra Dulgheru retired with a right shoulder injury while trailing 6-3, 4-1 on Thursday.
